title: Realty regulator: Not yet!
text:
Like this story, share it with millions of investors on M3 Realty regulator: Not yet! The real estate regulator bill may miss its date with the upcoming monsoon session of parliament, the good news is it may carry more punch from imprisonment of builders to holding the centre and state governments accountable. Nayantar Rai of Prime Property has more details. Post your opinion here Prime Property
